#. Tag: title
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting Usage Limits"
msgstr "設定使用限制"

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&PRODUCT; provides several administrator control points for capping resource"
" usage by users. Some of these limits are global configuration parameters. "
"Others are applied at the ROOT domain and may be overridden on a per-account"
" basis."
msgstr "&PRODUCT;提供多個管理者控制點給隱藏資源使用率，有些限制是廣域設定參數，其他應用在ROOT網域及無視每個帳戶的基礎"

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Aggregate limits may be set on a per-domain basis. For example, you may "
"limit a domain and all subdomains to the creation of 100 VMs."
msgstr "累積極限可能會在每個網域基礎上設定，例如，您可以限制網域，並且所有子網域只能建立100VM"

